  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16333,
    "dDurationMs": 3300,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and even this world ending nuclear bomb."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 19667,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But first, we're gonna start off with\na single block of TNT."
